Module JPM_Exchange
Package finance

Class Exchange

java.lang.Object
finance.Exchange
All Implemented Interfaces:
WeightedDigraph
public class Exchange
extends java.lang.Object
implements WeightedDigraph
This class builds an exchange for time spreads. It does so implementing WeightedDigraph interface. Indeed, an exchange is a graph, where months are veritces and futures the edges.
Author:
Guglielmo Del Sarto
